#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.61"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.61:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 7. Paṭhamaāmakadhaññapeyyālavagga → āmakadhaññapeyyāle paṭhamavaggo (s1-3) | vaggo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.61:0.2"
msgid "7. Paṭhamaāmakadhaññapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "7. Abbreviated Texts on Raw Grain"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.61:0.3"
msgid "61. Aññatrasutta"
msgstr "61. Not Human"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.466"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.61:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā parittaṃ nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsuṃ āropetvā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha, picking up a little bit of dirt under his fingernail, "
"addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn56.61:1.2"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.61:1.3"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yo vāyaṃ mayā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito, "
"ayaṃ vā mahāpathavī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the little bit of dirt under my fingernail, or this great "
"earth?”"

msgctxt "sn56.61:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—mahāpathavī; appamattakāyaṃ bhagavatā "
"paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the great earth is certainly more. The little bit of dirt under your "
"fingernail is tiny."

msgctxt "sn56.61:1.5"
msgid ""
"Saṅkhampi na upeti, upanidhampi na upeti, kalabhāgampi na upeti mahāpathaviṃ "
"upanidhāya bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the great earth, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even "
"a fraction.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: manussehi → manussesu (si, mr)
msgctxt "sn56.61:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appamattakā te sattā ye manussesu paccājāyanti; "
"atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye aññatra manussehi paccājāyanti."
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, the sentient beings reborn as humans are few, while those "
"not reborn as humans are many."

msgctxt "sn56.61:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn56.61:2.3"
msgid "Adiṭṭhattā, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ."
msgstr "It’s because they haven’t seen the four noble truths."

msgctxt "sn56.61:2.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.61:2.5"
msgid ""
"Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya "
"ariyasaccassa."
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.61:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.61:3.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
